iOS (Ver.11 onwards) gives Users the option of opting out of specific Interest-Based Ads. 
Users can also opt out of sharing their location data. For details, please refer to the Privacy Policy. 
Please note that you can withdraw your consent at any time. For details, please check your in-game settings.

Android gives Users the option of opting out of specific Interest-Based Ads via their device settings. 
Users can also opt out of sharing their location data. 
For details, please refer to the Privacy Policy. 
Please note that you can withdraw your consent at any time. 
For details, please check your in-game settings.
